title: Clear Springs overcomes late push from Friendswood to win key match
text:
Clear Springs overcomes late push from Friendswood to win key match 
FRIENDS WOOD - Just when it looked like the Friendswood Lady Mustangs were going to rally on their home court, the Clear Springs Chargers kept it together and came from behind in the match-deciding final game and won the match 27-25, 25-19, 21-25, 25-21 in a key District 24-6A contest on Tuesday.
